{"tid":2080423,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃店大撚晒?] 中西區-黃店Salon中晒伏","createTime":"2020-06-26T11:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T19:53:49.000Z","uid":249123,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9c417acffcb5d3a9a0b3f7bd0c4b2b75fc4ffcd8","tid":2080423,"uid":249123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"[借朋友AC]<br />\n長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太撚嬲！<br />\n<br />\n今日去中西區剪頭髮，間野叫<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Salon Z_we_</span></span></strong>，見佢係黃店所以想試試佢。由於唔係剪開，佢地就介紹咗(簡稱:B哥)幫我剪頭髮。<br />\n<br />\n一開始比咗張參考圖佢睇，佢就問我側邊剷青洗唔洗剷到好貼，我就話<ins>唔洗</ins>。<br />\n因為大家都鐘意睇波，有共同話題，一開頭都有講有笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲幾好禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n循例洗完頭之後，B哥開始幫我剷青，用電剷推完，再用梳同鉸剪修，之後又再用電剷推，不斷翻手，愈剷愈青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋪頭唔大，玻璃鏡反射可以清晰見到其他髮型師既舉動。剪髮期間，見到第二位男髮型師(長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)不時望住我偷笑，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">成個過程比我感覺到好唔尊重客人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪咗一個鐘，髮完嘅時候B哥攞塊鏡比我睇後面，不過唔太清楚。因為不受尊重，比完錢就想拿拿臨走人。<br />\n返到屋企照一照，發現後面同側邊<ins>一達達</ins>好離譜，即刻返去叫B哥幫我修修。<br />\n<br />\n返番鋪頭，B哥見到話係<span style=\"color: red;\">暗瘡</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">頭型</span>影響會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問我以前係咪剷到好貼，好貼先見唔到洞洞。(但我極少剷到好貼，一開頭已經利申唔好咁貼)<br />\n<br />\n當B哥幫我修剪嘅時候，長毛嘅客人唔知做緊色定電髮，所以長毛有時間坐喺我哋後面休息。<ins>本身見佢低頭族打緊字，之後遞起手機對住我，懷疑佢影相或拍片。</ins>當我望向佢既時候，佢就會移左移右，影完又做返低頭族望住手機笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最後我只想講：藍黃係政見，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇職業操守就係冇職業操守</span></span></strong>。就係以為係同路人先幫襯，唔係話黃店做得唔好都要忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ce1b4cad7420ead289c400523c3003d94f35db","tid":2080423,"uid":199893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"真心剷得好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fa02d07773645f728c12684e89a037c7005cef","tid":2080423,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"衰過一次就永不錄用啦"},{"pid":"c0d15ccc5d5ef00ad79dbb87156619040dd6f160","tid":2080423,"uid":249123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45fa02d07773645f728c12684e89a037c7005cef","tid":2080423,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"衰過一次就永不錄用啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"就係第一次都奶晒嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2014651126666183a9be65c1d91b00428710452b","tid":2080423,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"傻閪黃圈"},{"pid":"44acdc837668a0536e6cb9c47bf6f9ef6010a286","tid":2080423,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"直接開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6828688013b3df84babefe47c3101e1216dad24","tid":2080423,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"直接開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966425bf66208cc17a12727eb6872e50c9b82ca4","tid":2080423,"uid":249123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6828688013b3df84babefe47c3101e1216dad24","tid":2080423,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"直接開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"開咗啦清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5268e286392227b58f5d247ec4cf0aae952da8d","tid":2080423,"uid":40382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:41:23.000Z","msg":"我都係堅尼地城做，你聽日有時間去一去我舖頭，我幫你睇下有冇得執，唔收你錢， 不過我唔知道點樣pm卡片畀你， 等我搵搵先"},{"pid":"622b1b1fbceb82ffe2feb0c50e16a2173d6cf50a","tid":2080423,"uid":40382,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRAu60Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRAu60Y.jpg&h=77a234a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先唔理你頭骨適唔適合剪咁貼，但係頸毛都未剷乾淨係唔可以原諒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnPzyGs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnPzyGs.jpg&h=077fb109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩邊青位鴛鴦，後部分undercut表現生硬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcHtC8x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcHtC8x.jpg&h=dd74a0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅圈嗰啲點點有機會係頭髮生長嘅密度唔同所以有呢個情況,唔知咁貼就冇乜所謂或者推盡啲推白佢， 紫色圈好明顯條的水都未剪得乾淨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFgNTHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFgNTHw.jpg&h=884e34b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剪完好似一個蓋<br />\n呢度冇得pm,我留tg畀你,你有興趣就搵我"},{"pid":"768e751550224d7036e1f95faae7aae894c4602e","tid":2080423,"uid":40382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"你可以放你張參考圖上嚟大家睇睇"},{"pid":"d304e5f4a0fa13a927940937d2331c099dd43a01","tid":2080423,"uid":34606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"本身都想試吓係呢間salon剪頭髮，果陣仲見都幾多正評，過年前想去剪但見入面勁多客好full就放棄咗，估唔到有伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自從發現之前剪開嘅係藍店就想近近地搵間黃嘅剪髮但未搵到，睇黎呢間都唔洗試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 